 cap1_h:"Izinhlelo ze-agentic ezenza umsebenzi",cap1_p:"Hhayi ama-chatbot anamathiselwe ohlangothini. Ama-ejenti azimele aphethe wonke amageja emsebenzi — afunda, anquma, enze, adlulisele — ezingxenyeni zebhizinisi lakho ezishukumisa inombolo ngempela.",
 cap2_h:"Ukwakheka kwe-AI-native",cap2_p:"Asenzi ngokuzenzakalelayo ishadi elidala lenhlangano. Silidweba kabusha. Inhlakanipho isenkabeni yendlela inkampani esebenza ngayo, futhi yonke inqubo yakhelwe umhlaba lapho umshini wenza uhlaka lokuqala lwakho konke.",
 cap3_h:"Isikhundla somkhakha ongasivikela",cap3_p:"Ukuba AI-native kunenzuzo kuphela uma imakethe yazi ukuthi nguwe. Sakha ubufakazi, isikhundla, kanye nangempela yokusebenza okwenza ube yiphuzu lokubhekisa emkhakheni wakho — hhayi olandelayo.",
 cap4_h:"Izinqumo ezinqwabelanayo",cap4_p:"Izinhlelo ezingagcini nje ngokwenza — ziyafunda. Wonke umjikelezo ulola imodeli yebhizinisi lakho, ngakho ungqimba lokusebenza oluzoluqhuba ngekota elandelayo luhlakaniphile ngokulinganisekayo kunalolu olwanamuhla.",
 cap5_h:"Umsele okhula ngokuhamba kwesikhathi",cap5_p:"Igebe phakathi kwakho nemakethe akulona ukwethulwa — kuyindlela. Sakha inzuzo enqwabelanayo abancintisani abangeke bayithenge, bayiboleke, noma bayikopishe, ngoba iphila endleleni osebenza ngayo, hhayi kulokho onakho.",
 method_eye:"Indlela",method_re:"RE-",method_actt:"ACTT",method_dim:" — indlela inkampani eba ngayo the ONE.",
 method_lede:"Injini yokuguqula ephindaphindekayo. Hhayi i-workshop. Indlela esuka lapho ukhona iye phambili emkhakheni wakho.",
 actt_a:"Architecture",actt_ad:"Sidweba imodeli yokusebenza ye-AI-native kusukela ezisekelweni.",
 actt_c:"Capability",actt_cd:"Simisa ama-ejenti nezinhlelo ezenza umsebenzi.",
